{"tid":1451031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後發夢同我一人帶一樣證明自己唔係狗嘅野！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:30:04.000Z","uid":23727,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"76aa9c492b66750df3f3a9efcdba65a249e4ea32","tid":1451031,"uid":23727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:23.000Z","msg":"學生嘅，同我放番張學生證入銀包<br />\n番緊工嘅就袋番張員工證，<br />\n冇員工證嘅就袋啲乜乜柒柒公司出糧證明etc<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反正一人帶一樣證明自己唔係狗嘅野！！！</span><br />\n但盡量唔好淨係袋啲乜柒綠卡、保安卡呢啲毅進仔都考得到嘅野！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係前線見到啲鬼鬼地嘅人就幾個人撳低左佢先，然後叫佢證明自己唔係狗。證明唔到嘅就打佢老母臭屄！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有殺錯冇放過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係冇野證明到嘅話就唔該唔好咁鬼，唔好戴earphone，或者乾脆唔好行咁前！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"dde64be374558f0e872819ce73b6574c914ebf57","tid":1451031,"uid":23727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"我屌撚爆晒你地對眼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de4763080f1ae0ff2dc775f3136afafed5cd50c","tid":1451031,"uid":23727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"食屎狗"},{"pid":"5656e9b9f834e172429458794ec6040b060248ab","tid":1451031,"uid":23727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:16:45.000Z","msg":"全部黑警同我含撚死"},{"pid":"b16433b256f51365890fcab0c382184ed6ff705d","tid":1451031,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係